{"tid":1393161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會譴責下周一罷工行動籲僱員堅守崗位","createTime":"2019-08-01T03:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T05:40:51.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3d52a8b71f5162d068f6858cc72984ca4eec78a7","tid":1393161,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:59:14.000Z","msg":"有網民發起8月5日全港罷工、罷課、罷市，並在七區集會，要求政府回應示威者五大訴求。工聯會理事長黃國批評，示威者借修例風波，企圖癱瘓香港社會正常運作，威脅特區政府，要予以反對及譴責。鐵路工會聯合會副主席譚建釗指，鐵路前線員工壓力上升，有人被無理指責，自己亦受網絡欺凌、起底，呼籲示威者要和平理性表達意見。工聯會呼籲僱員堅守崗位，特別是交通運輸、公共服務業及公務員。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，職工盟主席吳敏兒在一個電台節目表示，職工盟經商討後同意支持罷工行動，強調基本法列明市民有罷工權利，她說，目前難以掌握參與人數，但相信罷工是較斯文的方式表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工會反對罷工，維護政權，真係天下奇聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef210aff0e3f78711e47ec4bf8c68e5d954f9be","tid":1393161,"uid":158613,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:01:16.000Z","msg":"尋日8球波，工聯會有冇開門？"},{"pid":"13dc88faed0bfd2d45e4bee49abc64a044afc9b3","tid":1393161,"uid":173356,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c261798578a824fdd078bb0bd26815640aedef7c","tid":1393161,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:06:31.000Z","msg":"ok 收到"},{"pid":"794b4977c528604e3e2ad9d633fefcdeceb4f85c","tid":1393161,"uid":72058,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cd21c4efcd6f791852d3318136ceece0ceb07e","tid":1393161,"uid":1612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UfXqfrD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfXqfrD.png&h=8f3dee07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vZtQrBo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna